[Notice]
-Swap Start 22th Dec.
-Holders of STRAX will receive 10 STRAT tokens for each STRAX token (10:1 ratio) during the Stratis Token Swap.
-Upbit, Binance is scheduled to support on the 24th Dec.
-Preliminary discussions with all exchanges have been completed.
-The token swap period is until December 28, 2024, and token swaps are not possible after the deadline.
-All holders should use the relevant exchange, and personal wallet users should use the bridge.
